sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic

Class BasicAddressFieldWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic.BasicFieldWrapper
      • sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic.BasicAddressFieldWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddressField, Field

    public class BasicAddressFieldWrapper
extends BasicFieldWrapper
implements AddressField
    A wrapper for a Field which adds getValue() methods returning Addresses. Must be a wrapper since the concrete type of the Field implementation will not be, for example, a BasicAddressField because, for simplicity, we don't currently understand pointer types in the Type system.
